"選擇 :guilabel:`圖片` 會在 :ref:`表單檢視畫面 <studio/views/general/form>` "
"的右上角，新增一個 :ref:`圖片欄位 <studio/fields/simple-fields-image>` 。"

#: ../../content/applications/studio/models_modules_apps.rst:126
